result:
<!-- 修改命令集 -->
<!-- style="top: 20px;" -->
  <a-modal
    title="选择地图"
    centered
    :width="500"
    v-model="visible"
    @ok="showCmd"
    v-preventReClick
    :destroyOnClose="true"
    :maskClosable = "false"
  >
  <a-form :form="form">
   <a-form-item label="地图" :labelCol="labelCol" :wrapperCol="wrapperCol">
        <a-select
            showSearch
            placeholder="非必选"
            optionFilterProp="children"
            @change="changeMap($event)"
            v-decorator="['mapId']"
        >
          <a-select-option
           v-for="(item ,key) in mapList"
           :key="key"
           :value="item.id">
              {{item.mapName}}
            </a-select-option>
        </a-select>
  </a-form-item>
   </a-form>
    <cmd-list @getCmdId="getCmdId" ref="cmd"></cmd-list>
  </a-modal>
